# Cursor Rules — LocalForge Integration

## Local Workflow Runner
This project uses LocalForge for multi-step pipelines.
Run `python -m localforge run <recipe> --auto-approve` for automated workflows.

## Available Commands
- `python -m localforge list` — List available recipes
- `python -m localforge health` — Check service status
- `python -m localforge run <recipe> --list-inputs` — See recipe inputs

## Key Recipes
- `recipes/examples/game-sprite.yaml` — Generate sprites
- `recipes/examples/tileset.yaml` — Generate tileable textures
- `recipes/examples/music-track.yaml` — Generate music
- `recipes/examples/3d-model.yaml` — Generate 3D models
